@*
   _OfflineSyncBadge.cshtml — Indicateur de synchronisation (header)

   3 états gérés via [data-state] :
   - online   : point vert, "En ligne"
   - syncing  : point orange pulsant, "Synchronisation 3/12"
   - offline  : point rouge, "Hors ligne — N en attente"

   Cliquable → ouvre le drawer _OfflineSyncDrawer (#lc-sync-drawer)
*@
<button type="button"
        class="lc-sync-status"
        data-sync-status
        data-state="online"
        data-sync-open
        aria-label="Statut de synchronisation"
        aria-haspopup="dialog">
    <span class="lc-sync-status__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="lc-sync-status__label">En ligne</span>
</button>
